Description: Next-generation spreadsheet with AI-powered collaboration
 Spreadsheet Moment is a revolutionary spreadsheet application that combines
 tensor-based computation, natural language processing, and real-time
 collaboration. Features include:
  - Tensor operations with automatic differentiation
  - NLP cell editor for natural language queries
  - Real-time multi-user collaboration
  - Temperature-based data propagation
  - Vector search for semantic cell discovery
  - Bio-inspired consensus algorithms
